				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 01 Mar 2018 16:42:09 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>RJB_R</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1229263</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This reminds me of my own SCP-1976 combined with King's <em>Needful Things</em>, in a good way. Loss of identity in a community is always a strong thing to write about and this captures that small-town paranoia perfectly.</p> 
				 	]]>
